      <title>Haste upgrade question...</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=beastlordbalance&amp;message.id=3283#M3283</link>
      <description>The issue of haste duration, haste potions, etc has come up for awhile among beastlords.  It has even been mentioned on the top 10 a few times as I recall.  Some want a group version, some are ok with the thought of longer duration, but there is another issue that I think we need to go over first.  &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Are you willing to see an increase in the mana cost of haste if it receives some upgrade(s)?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The change might not be % for % even, or it might be, or it might not even happen.  I just need to be sure that most beastlords understand that the mana cost likely would increase (especially if this goes to group) and that they still want such a change before I go further with this issue.</description>
